            "jpName": "テレビクルー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 48,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -8265153113115138747
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 451953002013028714
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8052444962177438272,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者B",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……おいおい、発言が強気すぎるだろ。\nナカヤマフェスタ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 5788415690032106508
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -3524557259799727607
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 288521202836389088,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者C",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "去年のウマ娘も、その前に挑んだ三冠ウマ娘\nだって、『凱旋門賞』には届かなかったんだ。\nなのに皐月を終えたばかりのウマ娘が……。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 127,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": -2185660023025291014
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": -4926382809131564151
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5783238786662941015,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "丸メガネの記者",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ナカヤマフェスタさん、\n一言よいでしょうか？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
