            "pathId": -4719451881296323988,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……エルが見せた一瞬の夢に\n私たちはとらわれている、とでも？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -6359478443707128906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -6676065206708645134
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1998010206231324417,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "丸メガネの記者",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ええ。そのうえで判断すべきです。\nエルコンドルパサーさんと\n同じ夢を掲げるべきか、否かを。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -4981590286795588896
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": 7171054960813578817
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6701032091969398250,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "丸メガネの記者",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "エルコンドルパサーさんと比べて、\nあなたの器は――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ええ、世界を獲れる器です",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 34
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": 5345198138444772529
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -8491381509509179649
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3074454477260025482,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "丸メガネの記者",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……！？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": 1437916228198498431
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 2518872656866303433
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -6887035112990393432
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5228255747803260687,
            "blockIdx": 34
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "すまねぇな、おせっかい焼きさん。\nんなこと私らにとっては\nどうでもいいことなんだわ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 36,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -3901823143589728200
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": 5045729462876439353
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -5505888232963501855
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3566490780617522559,
            "blockIdx": 35
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "アンタが言うように私とエルじゃ、\n元から持っている才能が違う。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 37,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -6453498463761916224
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -8162777251313186074
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2661121338235914268,
            "blockIdx": 36
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "だけどな、\nやれ不可能だ、やめろだの。\n勝手に諦めてんじゃねぇよ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 38,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -6680305808976720545
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 808687029629124649
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8305555549978678685,
            "blockIdx": 37
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どうせなら一緒に夢を追いかけようぜ。\nロマンを求めるなら、地に足つけず、\n浮かれるくらいでちょうどいい。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 39,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -2787877292943273387
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": -4293880486059272274
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7262978125100092680,
            "blockIdx": 38
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "さあ、希望を見ろよ。\n――次のダービーで。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 40,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": 5923529165043167669
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -6110117318985687020
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6911834592945400215,
            "blockIdx": 39
        },
